Procedure
1. Download and install Keil uVision software.
2. Open Keil software.
3. Create a new project.
4. Select the 8051 microcontroller.
5. Create a new assembly file.
6. Write the simple assembly language program.
7. Save the file with .asm extension.
8. Build the program.
9. Run the simulation and observe the output.

Program
----------------------
MOV A,#05H
MOV R0,#03H
ADD A,R0
END
